ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
Employee attrition impacts organizational stability, productivity, and hiring costs. This project analyzes HR employee data to understand attrition patterns and identify key factors influencing employee turnover using Power BI.
The analysis focuses on workforce composition, tenure, job roles, income levels, and satisfaction metrics to provide data-driven insights for HR decision-making.

ðŸŽ¯ Objective
-> Analyze overall employee attrition and workforce distribution.
-> Identify key attrition drivers across departments, job roles, tenure, and income.
-> Evaluate the impact of job satisfaction and work-life balance on attrition.
-> Provide actionable insights to support employee retention strategies.

ðŸ“‚ Dataset
Source: IBM HR Analytics Employee Attrition Dataset
Format: CSV
Description: Contains employee demographics, job roles, department details, income, tenure, job satisfaction, work-life balance, and attrition status (Yes/No).

